-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository contains 3 data sets. It is pretty big so it may be worthwhile
to just take the parts you need as you need them rather than clone the lot.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Synthetic metagenome referenced in the GroopM paper:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This folder contains the synthetic metagenomes used in the validation of GroopM
It includes the raw reads used in our assembly + our contigs (produced using
Velvet + defaults) + GroopM bin assignments AND MORE!

See the README in this folder for details.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Infant gut microbiome referenced in the GroopM paper:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This folder contains a GroopM-based analysis of data produced for:

Time series community genomics analysis reveals rapid shifts in bacterial
species, strains, and phage during infant gut colonization. Itai Sharon, Michael
J. Morowitz, Brian C. Thomas, Elizabeth K. Costello, David A. Relman and Jillian
F. Banfield. Genome Res. 2013. 23: 111-120.

This folder contains our contigs (produced using SPAdes + deafults) + GroopM bin
assignments.

See the README in this folder for details.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
